    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Honest project car/parts car being sold in poor condition. It shows heavy wear inside and out, has multiple cosmetic flaws, and should be expected to need mechanical work and deferred maintenance before it can be considered dependable. Best suited for someone looking for a fixer-upper, restoration candidate, or donor vehicle rather than a turn-key daily driver.",
