      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s priced to be an easy, budget-friendly buy. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a practical option for someone after cheap wheels, a first runabout, or a tidy project to improve over time. If you want something affordable with plenty of life left for the right owner, this could be a great fit. Sensibly priced and worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project with strong utility and plenty of upside for the next owner. The drivetrain is complete, the engine bay is mechanically straightforward, and it fires up and runs, making it a great candidate for a fixer-upper, commuter build, or parts/support platform. Shows its age cosmetically and will need attention consistent with a well-used vehicle, but it has the kind of simple, serviceable setup that DIY owners appreciate. If you want an affordable car with good bones and room to sort to your standards, this is a compelling buy.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap way into a running car. Used and rough, but priced to move. Honest value. Grab it before it\u2019s gone.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough for the right buyer, this car has the kind of lived-in character you can\u2019t fake. It\u2019s the sort of vehicle that still turns a simple drive into a story, with a presence that suggests plenty of road left for someone ready to make it their own. Whether you\u2019re after an inexpensive runabout, a hands-on project, or just a machine with personality, this one offers a rare chance to step into ownership without breaking the bank. Honest, full of potential, and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers a practical entry point for anyone seeking low-cost transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and wear, but it still presents strong value at this price point for a buyer who wants dependable basic motoring without a major investment. A smart choice for budget-conscious shoppers looking for honest value.",
      "price": 5495.0,
